speech.p:
asked the Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs (1) what documents Her Majesty's Government still have in their possession concerning people who held high office in the Nazi Party or Government of Germany prior to 1945; and to what extent they are prepared to permit public access to these documents;

(2) until what date documents concerning the pre-1945 activities of people

holding high office in the Nazi Party or Government of Germany were in the sole possession of the war-time Allied Powers; and when these were made available by Her Majesty's Government to the West German Government.
